songs.title: Makey Makeover
songs.lyrics:
[REBECCA]
It's a makeover, makey makeover
It's a makey makey makey makey makey makeover
Old you in the garbage
New you in display case
Old you was a diaper
New you is a diamond
Makeover, it's a makey makeover
It's a makey lakey wakey fakey bakey makeover

Process...
Process...
Reveal!
Reveal!
Hairs! Nailies!
Sparkle magic horse!
Makeover, it's a makey makeover
It's a makey lakey wakey fakey bakey cakey rakey nakey
I had a stroke
I had a stroke
I had a stroke
I had a stroke
